This is such a sweet movie, with endearing characters that I just couldn't believe that the ending was so unsatisfying. Give me a tidy, happy ending with a kiss & the prospect of marriage please,not some open ended silliness.
This show was really cute.  The story had many sweet and funny moments.  I especially liked that the English subtitles were excellent.
10 episode, 3 discs japan drama (romantic comedy), with Kim Tae Hee was very good and i enjoyed it. i ordered the $28.99 one. english subs were good.
